=======================
Release Date		: November 03, 2005
Author                  : [AF]Meelo
E-mail Address          : kromano@shaw.ca
Web Site		: www.ztgames.com
Server Hosting Map	: 63.208.142.66:27015
Other Files by Author	: cs_escher, de_aardvark
Misc Author Info	: Keep your fork. There's pie!
Additional Credits	: Most of the base textures I used were from Mayang's
                          Free Texture Library: http://www.mayang.com/textures/

Description             : A Doom inspired defusal map. Spent a number of hours
			  building custom models and textures for it.

Instructions		: Place the .BSP and .NAV in your cstrike/maps folder
		 (i.e C:\Steam\SteamApps\username\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps)

======================

* Play Information *

Game			: Counter-Strike: Source
Bots                    : Bots should navigate the entire map, relatively problem free
New Sounds              : No, sadly.
New Graphics            : Yes. Roughly 50% or so of the textures in the map were
		          made by me as well as about a dozen new props.

* Construction *

Base                    : New level, inspired from Doom 3 (and some of the props
			  from Fallout)
Build Time              : Uhhh, maybe 24-48 hours over the course of a week or two.
Editor(s) used          : Hammer 4.0, 3ds Max 5.1, Photoshop 7.0
Known Bugs              : None that I know of.
